          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 sm:h-20 sm:w-20 md:h-24 md:w-24 lg:h-28 lg:w-28 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
